claim_reports.verdict_summary: The evidence presents a mixed view on whether autophagy occurs during a juice cleanse. A medium reliability source indicates that juice cleanses do not effectively induce autophagy due to the intake of calories and nutrients. However, other sources suggest that a juice cleanse may trigger autophagy due to reduced caloric intake, particularly within 24-48 hours. This inconsistency highlights the need for further research.

refutes.title: Autophagy Explained: The Only Real Way To Cleanse Your Body
